        <abstract>
            <p>CD guessed Carruthers was stirred up by Owen. Disgraceful treatment of Bentham.</p> 
<p>Work on <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Coral reefs</hi> stops his doing anything of real interest.</p> 
            <p>Asa Gray’s letter. CD has acknowledged the honour [honorary membership in the Boston Soc. Nat. Hist.].</p>
            <p>"What a demon on earth Owen is. I do hate him."</p>
        </abstract>
